          I would like to express my extreme satisfaction on the projects where our company (www.tranz-life.com) engaged Digital Landscape for strategic consulting and development of healthcare software. The technical team did a very professional job for the development of various software we required for our commercial operation such as patient access software and virtual calling tools. The team in Digital Landscape is highly qualified and experienced in all major fields of IT and specializes in; software and app development, networking, Artificial Intelligence (AI) & Machine Learning (ML), Business Intelligence (BI) and Software/Data Security. We also found the leadership team in Digital Landscape is highly capable of envisaging the upcoming challenges to be faced by the healthcare industry as a result of recent COVID pandemic and for that Digital Landscape is applying AI and ML solutions through state-of-the-art technology for patient support 24/7 through ‘virtual physician’. Tranz-Life is a primary solution provider to the healthcare industry in commercial and clinical outsourcing services. The broader areas of Tranz-Life’s activities include Contract Sales Organization (CSO), Contract Research Organization (CRO), Patient Support programs and Market Access. We would like to recommend Digital Landscape for IT solutions, especially for software/app development . We look forward to working with them in future projects.
